A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Matt Money Smith break down where each of the 32 teams fall in the Power rank- oh wait, wrong show. We recap every single upcoming game for Week 4 starting with the primetime games. Brady returns to New England!
